summary:
I am a young insurance industry professional with 2.5 years of experience working at Swiss Re.
I come from Slovakia, but I have spent most of my life living abroad, in – Sweden, South Africa, Macedonia & the Netherlands.
I am fluent in: English, Russian, Slovak and Czech.
Currently I am learning Italian.
I am flexible, friendly, hard-working, diligent, and eager to learn.
I am looking forward to starting a career in Human Resurces or Cusomer Success.
